  <span id="freeText16455084357680139559" style="display:none">Would you move into a house that has pages and pages of rules? Where the questions ask you things that you couldn't live without? Questions about everything person? Also, you can't have kids/pets/make a mess?<br><a href="http://s926.photobucket.com/user/bookqueenshelby/media/tumblr_nszwq9l1aQ1sfysqqo1_500_zpsu0p8gag6.gif.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
